{
  "texts": [
    "The last layer of our VGG-19 model is replaced with the SoftMax classification Function.",
    "Two hidden layers containing 4096 and 512 units are present before the SoftMax output function.",
    "L2 regularization was applied to all FCLs except the dropout layer to prevent overfitting during the fine-tuning procedure.",
    "Data fusion was utilized in a variety of machine learning and CV tasks in the literature [51].",
    "The number of feature vectors generated by two feature extractors is 14,096 and 13,780, respectively."
  ]
}